        <div class="span-3">
          <img style="width:60%; float: center; margin-top:5px;" src="images/icon-06.png">
        </div>
        <div class="span-20">
          <h3><b>5. We're Happy When You Are</b></h3>
          <ul>
            <li>We care. We want to make sure you are happy with the value you get from RubyNow.</li>
            <li>We respond promptly to all questions and comments you might have.</li>
          </ul>

          
          <%= link_to "Post to RubyNow",    '/post/jobs/new', class:"button inline", title:"Post Now", style:"float: right;" %>
